{"tid":1861192,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[#1睇懶人包] 網購外科口罩集中討論130","createTime":"2020-02-04T04:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T19:37:00.000Z","uid":11208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"01c1331120dbdc8908146934ac6347788943c3be","tid":1861192,"uid":11208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:32:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>內容及資料僅供參考，投資涉及風險，口罩價格可升亦可跌，甚至變成亳無價值。旅客在決定是否購買有關口罩之前應先閱讀有關風險評估，以了解該建議發售之詳細資料，並應就本身的財務、其他狀況及需要，詳細考慮並決定購買有關口罩是否切合本身特定的需要，若有需要更應咨詢其他專業意見，方可作出有關購買決定。<br />\n忠告：親自買罩 咪俾錢炒狗</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家基本上得返日本Amazon有現貨賣，<br />\n所以唔好買太多，到時禁運就真係攬炒一鑊熟。<br />\n<br />\n問呢個得唔得嘅，最少睇曬前2/3個post嘅圖。<br />\n<br />\n做開團團長嘅，求下你，你開個tg,wts gp出嚟畀人join，夠數就關link。<br />\n<br />\n間間集運都爆，唔好再問邊間快啲邊間好用，根本就無人知。<br />\n<br />\n記得留意返集運公司對體積重收費同要求，隨時運費貴過口罩本身，重有拒收嘅風險存在。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>麻煩大家Amazon唔好再用殘體字 有得揀英文/日文</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ee1e8b62186f9583eb6e020a7651c606a41afa65","tid":1861192,"uid":133024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8afa1005224e34bc78870615522bbc7027bf6d2c","tid":1861192,"uid":73033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee1e8b62186f9583eb6e020a7651c606a41afa65","tid":1861192,"uid":133024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35f170a1acbaac206